\frametitle{Variable-coefficient advection}


{\blue Color equation:}

\[
q_t(x,t) + u(x) q_x(x,t) = 0.
\]


Can be rewriten as a {\blue balance law}\\
\hhsp (conservation law plus source term):

\[
q_t(x,t) + (u(x) q(x,t))_x = u'(x)q(x,t)
\]

Will revisit different forms when studying numerical methods.




